ObjectStates.Name: Bag
ObjectStates.Description: Include in the game if you plan to use the optional combat rules (#15 in the rulebook) and/or the Rastur (#16).

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
1) Mix the "?" counters and put one in each "?" box on the map, removing the remaining ones from the game.
2) Mix the 'first contact' (IOU) markers and put one in each culture box on the side of the board.
3) Each player rolls two dice; highest roller selects species with selection proceeding clockwise.
4) Each player receives 20$ for every player.
